<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Case the 'adapter' was assigned in config the method Zend_Http_Client::getAdapter() should verify if the o adapter is null and assign in next.
Sample code below.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function getAdapter()
{
   if (null === $this-&gt;adapter) {
       $this-&gt;setAdapter($this-&gt;config['adapter']);
   }

    return $this-&gt;adapter;
}
</code></pre>

